ActEmergency Management Act
SubjectOrder No. 174 - (Manitoba) Provincial Emergency Financial Assistance Order
PrecisPROVINCIAL EMERGENCY FINANCIAL ASSISTANCE ORDER NO. 174 which makes a declaration of federal concern and authorizes financial assistance to the province of MANITOBA with respect to the RAINSTORM and FLOODING that affected the Western and Parkland regions and caused damage to private property, small businesses, farms and infrastructure from June 21 to 25, 2013.
